data.description: THIS CHARMING PROPERTY OFFERS AN OPEN FAMILY ROOM, WITH THE KITCHEN FLOWING SEAMLESSLY INTO THE DINING ROOM, PROVIDING A LOVELY VIEW OF THE GREAT BACKYARD. THE SPACIOUS BACKYARD IS PERFECT FOR ENTERTAINING LITTLE ONES AND FUR BABIES, AS WELL AS HOSTING FAMILY AND FRIENDS GATHERINGS.  THERE IS EVEN ENOUGH ROOM TO ADD A SWIMMING POOL IF DESIRED. THE UPSTAIRS FLEX ROOM IS A VERSATILE SPACE THAT CAN BE USED AS AN OFFICE, PLAYROOM, COMPUTER ROOM, OR EVEN A MOVIE ROOM. DON'T MISS THE OPPORTUNITY TO MAKE THIS HOUSE YOUR HOME. PROPERTY FEATURES 3 BEDROOMS, 2 BATHROOMS AND 2 CAR GARAGE.  CONVENIENTLY LOCATED JUST A FEW MINUTES FROM SUGAR LAND AND WITH EASY ACCESS TO THE FORT BEND TOLL, THIS HOME OFFERS THE PERFECT COMBINATION OF COMFORT AND ACCESSIBILITY.
